{"word":"ἔκπλοος","slug":"ἔκπλοος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἔκπλοος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐκπλέω'><el>ἐκπλέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a sailing out, leaving port</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a passage out, entrance of a harbour</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}